summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; approving final plans for a residential planned unit development of certain property on an RS 9600 zone at 7500 Seward Park Avenue South (Petition of Planning Commission re Caroline Kline Galland Home, C.F. 281359 and C.F. 2728701), and amending Plat 74W, page 175, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300.
